Greece Euro Exit Isn’t Being Mulled, Flosbach Tells Handelsblatt

-- B y   R a g n h i l d   K j e t l a n d
-- 
2011-09-07T17:16:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/greece-euro-exit-isn-t-being-mulled-flosbach-tells-handelsblatt.html
Klaus-Peter Flosbach, the financial
policy spokesman in parliament for  Angela Merkel ’s Christian
Democratic Union party, said ousting  Greece  from the euro area
isn’t being considered,  Handelsblatt  reported.  Friedrich Merz , another CDU member, said that an orderly
withdrawal from the currency union would make sense for Greece,
the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story: Ragnhild Kjetland in
Frankfurt at   rkjetland@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  